texts.text: >Beyond the door is a room with a high ceiling.
>You gaze up at a large, solemn statue.
This is Gozu-Tennoh, leader of the Mantra Army.
You have returned to me, Thor.
Demon Users, I must welcome you as well.
His aura is enormous. He's no average demon.
I lead demons and seek to build a nation of raw power.
One cannot command hellish fiends with average strength.
You walked a different path from my subordinate of the same name,
and in so doing grew strong.
In choosing this lonely road, you strived to succeed unaided,
and you walked with conviction. A commendable feat.
It is only in a mighty commander grasping everything in one fist...
Only through them may the weak...
unleash their power, under the direction of a confident leader.
Not necessarily true? You cannot say that as you are now.
and my wish to revive a nation built on brawn is within my grasp.
I shall wield this mighty army to realize our old wish: a world...
and our Mantra Army reigns forever.
If you wish to fight alongside the Mantra Army,
I will have no choice but to demonstrate my true strength.
I am Thor, the lone warrior. I will reach the top on my own.
If you and the Mantra Army extol the path to real power,
then I must take up my hammer.
Come. Let us have a fair fight, Gozu-Tennoh!
My might shall prove the righteousness of my path!
I say again, do not interfere!
>Thor warns [sys user_name] and the others then rushes forward.
Mantra Army, show him your unrivaled might.
Thor and Gozu-Tennoh's forces are, for now,
>Thor slowly crushes more of his foes.
The Mantra Army and Gozu-Tennoh are being pushed back!
>Potent energy swirls around Thor's raised hammer!
Everyone, stand back! Gozu-Tennoh is breaking apart!
>He crumbles with a fierce, earth-shattering rumble.
>The former Gozu-Tennoh lies in a pile on the floor.
The Mantra Army was once without rival.
But this proves independence WAS the path to true strength.
It's over! The Mantra Army is finished!
Fret not. We shall not be defeated so easily.
> Red, spirit-like orbs of light rise from the demons.
Spiritual energy similar to your human consciousness.
Those robbed of too much die. Those doing the robbing grow strong.
was this mass of stolen Magatsuhi.
His broken body has been reborn.
It looks like it's returning to its original state!
>You and the rest can only watch in breathless awe.
It pleases me to see how much you have grown.
He's fully recovered... It's like nothing ever happened.
Hmm... No, he's not the same.
That was a fine tussle, Thor. Now, I will show you real might.
I am Gozu-Tennoh, leader of the great Mantra Army.
Vanquish me if you can, lone warrior Thor!
